Description:
listedAS Live a Beautiful Life
Nestled at the end of a quiet court, yet central to all the main amenities is this beautifully renovated flawless home that offers a lifestyle one can only dream of. Through the manicured front lawn and well-established rose garden you will instantly be impressed the moment you step inside
A warm and cozy formal lounge room with bay windows and double brick feature wall is the perfect setting for some quiet rest and recreation and connects to the formal dining and/or study room with built-in shelves
Comprising 3 spacious bedrooms with built-in robes, master with ensuite, luxurious main bathroom, renovated laundry with adjoining guest powder room
The superb kitchen and dining is complemented with 400mm stone benchtops with waterfall, soft close drawers and 900mm Westinghouse appliances complete with dishwasher. The bi-fold doors and window blend the inside with the outside giving you flexible and effortless entertaining options all day and all year round. Even the simplest act of making a coffee and being able to pass it outside to your loved one through the kitchen window makes it more enjoyable
Whats even more delightful is watching your kids play on the undercover deck, or run around on the luscious lawn while you tend to your vegie garden. Features ducted heating, evaporative cooling, roller shutters, shed, decking light, built-in BBQ and automatic irrigation system. The double garage is currently being used as a rumpus and games room. After a hard days work, reward yourself with fresh beer on tap
Be careful, your friends and family are going to come over more often once they realize you live here
Walking distance to St Mary Mackillop, Keilor Views, Keilor Downs College, busses, parks and a quick drive to Keilor Central, Taylors Lakes Shopping Centre and Calder Freeway
Be quick to enquire and inspect. This property will be sold before Auction.
Our signs are everywhere... winningAS
Note: Every care has been taken to verify the accuracy of the details in this advertisement, however we cannot guarantee its correctness. Prospective purchasers are requested to take such action as is necessary, to satisfy themselves of any pertinent matters.

Description:
Brand spanking new!
This brand new quality built home is nestled in the sought-after pocket of Kalkallo's Cloverton estate, surrounded by unlimited infrastructure such as shops, schools, medical clinics, transport, park-lands and much more!
You will be extremely impressed upon arrival with a wide welcoming entry to this open plan residence. The builder has definitely put in extra thought into utilizing space with four extremely large bedrooms.

Inspection is a must for this one!

Description:
Ex-Display with Refined Quality and Design Versatility
Boasting a long list of upgrades throughout and lush landscaped gardens all-round, this sensational ex-display home presents a turn-key family lifestyle opportunity surrounded by other high-quality dwellings in a convenient Cloverton pocket.
Beyond its bold facade, the expansive entrance foyer with towering 3m ceilings creates an immediate impression, together with an extra-large master bedroom with WIR and private ensuite, 3 additional bedrooms (BIRs) and stylish main bathroom.
Dual living zones further enhance the home's family credentials including a formal lounge/TV room together with a vast and versatile open-plan living/dining area accompanied by an on-trend kitchen complete with stone benchtops and island breakfast bar, walk-in pantry and Omega appliances (dishwasher, 900mm oven and gas cooktop).
Other stand-out features include ducted heating and evaporative cooling for all-seasons enjoyment, alarm system, quality flooring, large laundry, solar/gas hot water, efficient LED lighting and NBN connection.
Step outside to discover an al-fresco entertaining area and wide backyard garden with high fences all-round for exceptional privacy, plus the added appeal of a remote-control double garage with internal entry.
Walking distance to parkland, playground and the popular Dwyer Street Cafe, this Cloverton neighbourhood will also offer close proximity to the area's key masterplan amenities including the Merri Creek conservation area, a range of sports facilities, retail and dining precincts, future schools, as well as easy access now to both Donnybrook Station and Hume Freeway.
